"ACCELERATED HEALING" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect:	<victim>
Aggressive:	No
Cumulative:	No
Duration:	Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:	Healing

"Accelerated Healing" causes the recipient's body to heal itself at a
faster rate.
===========================================================================

