Aggressive:	Yes
Cumulative:	N/A
Duration:	Instantaneous
Type of spell:	Acid

"Acid stream" sends of stream of acid towards the victim, inflicting a
large amount of damage.  This spell also has the chance of causing the
victim to move much slower.
===========================================================================
