Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     Yes
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Enchantment

This spell permanently ages the victim, granting them all the accompanying
benefits and detriments of being older.
===========================================================================
