#
ANATOMY (&+REpic Skill&n)
===========================================================================
When an individual chooses to focus their expertise in this skill area, 
they gain the ability to direct their attacks at certain areas of the body, 
inducing some potentially nasty side effects. It is also rumored that those 
with a healing ability learn to become much more thorough at applying their 
craft.
===========================================================================

#
ANIMALIST 
===========================================================================
The Animalist specializes in the feral nature of his art. They are able
to summon larger pets, and can even take the form of certain animals.

Innate Abilities
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
31st level:     Charm Animal
41st level:     Shapechange

Spells
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
9th circle:     Greater Summon Beast
11th circle:    Essence of the Wolf

===========================================================================
See also: "GREATER SUMMON BEAST", "ESSENCE OF THE WOLF", "SHAPECHANGE",
          SHAMAN

