ARTIFACTS (General Information)
===========================================================================
Artifacts are ultimately powerful items on Duris. The artifacts grant the
wielder/wearer awesome powers. Currently there are twenty-five separate
artifacts, each one-of-a-kind. They are unique and only one of each can be
found in the game, EVER. This is only a list of the current artifacts, not
including uniques or iouns. 

&+LAvernus the life stealer&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n: 
Drains the life force of the victim and transfers it to the wielder.
Wraps the wielder in a shell of stone.
Surrounds its wearer in a shimmering globe of protection. 
Surrounds its wielder in a holy shield of force.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.
Protects the wielder from the elements.

&+LDoombringer the sword of chaos&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n: 
Brings down three elemental powers upon the foes of the wielder.
Empowers the wielder with the energy of the elements, allowing them to
score numerous extra hits on their opponent.
Protects the wielder from the elements.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.

&+ythe mace of the&n &+Learth&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n: 
Randomly brings the powers of the elemental plane of earth down upon 
the foes of the wielder. 
Enhances the senses of the wielder.
Conceals the wielder from mundane eyes.
Surrounds its wearer in a shimmering globe of protection.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.

&+Cthe sphere of &+Wwind&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n:
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.
Protects the wielder from the elements.
Surrounds its wielder in a holy shield of force.
Grants the wielder the power of flight.
When called, causes a great burst of wind to knock its wielder's foes
off their feet.

&+Lthe sword of &+Yfire &n&+rand flame&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n:
Randomly brings the powers of the elemental plane of fire down upon the
foes of the wielder.
Surrounds the wielder in a protective globe of fire.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.
Protects the wielder from the elements.

&+bthe orb of the &+gsea&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n:
Grants the wielder increased intelligence and constitution.
Allows the wielder to breath water.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.
Protects the wielder from the elements.
Banishes the wielder's foes back to &+bThe Elemental Plane Of Water&N.

&+ythe holy avenger of Ambran&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&n:
Smites foes of evil alignment down with its holy power.
Wards off physical and magical attacks from the wielder.
Surrounds its wielder in a holy shield of force.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.
Enhances the senses of the wielder.

&+Gthe holy mace of the effreeti&N
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&N
Calls down the holy wraith of the effreeti god Kossuth upon its wielders'
foes.
Protects its wielder from magical attacks.
Surrounds its wielder in a holy shield of force.
Surrounds the wielder in a protective globe of fire. 
Protects the wielder from the elements.
Increases the attack speed of the wielder.

&+cstaff&N &+Cof&N &+Bblue&N &+bflames&N
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&+RKnown Special Power(s)&N
Allows its master to call upon the powers of several arcane spells at will, 
with but a word.
Surrounds its wearer in a shimmering globe of protection.
Conceals the wielder from mundane eyes.

&+rthe unholy avenger named 'Bloodlust'&n
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
