===========================================================================
Area of effect: <group>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Protection

"Battle Ecstasy" allows the Anti-Paladin that casts it to gain power from
the bloodletting of his comrades. When the Anti-Paladin's group mates
inflict damage on the enemy in battle, he gains strength from their
bloodlust.
===========================================================================

#
"BATTLE-FORGER" "BATTLE FORGER" (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The Alchemists of the Battle-Forgers have enhanced their combat skills and 
through close study of their warrior comrades have taken on skills allowing 
them to survive and withstand hand to hand combat due to increased riposte
skill and the ability to switch targets.
===========================================================================

#
