So controlled and skilled are the Dreadlords their group holds its place
for battle in tight formations unrivalled amongst any other. Able to more
effectively command it's unholy forces the Dreadlord protects and enables
more than ever the more fragile of its combined mass to stand back from the
fray to be at their most deadly.
===========================================================================
