#
BLACKSMITH (Specialization)
===========================================================================
A more subdued and less violent subclass of the alchemist the blacksmith 
excels in crafting and forging, finding more enjoyment searching the land 
for various ores and minerals then engaging in warfare like his 
counter-part. 

Skills 
