BLINK (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster> 
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Generic

While in combat, the Shadowmage may escape damage by casting the spell
"Blink". By blinking out of existence for a fraction of a second, the enemy
will fumble their attack and possibly fall. If the foe is a caster, they
may abort an offensive spell mid-chant.
===========================================================================

#
"BLOOD REAVER" (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The Blood Reaver has mastered the use of pain and blood bonds using this
to create a number of new abilities. With its attention fully focused on
a victim the reaver will slowly but steadily drain the victim of his life
by presence alone. He may also link with a fellow group member to drain
or give life depending on how is hurt. It is a two-way bond.

Innate Abilities
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
31st level:	Drain Life

Spells
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
10th circle: Blood Alliance

===========================================================================
See also: REAVER, "BLOOD ALLIANCE", "DRAIN LIFE"

#
"BLOOD ALLIANCE"
===========================================================================
A Blood Reaver may find a willing target to have an alliance in blood with
them. Once they are linked, if one of them drops below 50% of their health
and the other has more than 70%, then damage to the weaker triggers some
transfer of hitpoints from the stronger to the weaker member. This spell
is usually used to link Blood Reavers with anti-paladins causing them to
form a dark and terrible evil plague. 
===========================================================================
See also: REAVER, "BLOOD REAVER"

#
"BLOOD SCENT" (Skill)
===========================================================================
The unholy corruption inherent within the Dreadlords feeds their lust for
blood. This gives them the ability to smell and sense the blood upon the
bodies of a wounded foe within enemy ranks as sure as they look within the
room. Syntax: scent
===========================================================================
See also: DREADLORD, SKILL_DREADLORD

