Area of effect: <room>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Fear

When cast, this spell causes the caster to assume the visage of the worst 
nightmare of everyone else in the room. The immense and sudden fear can
cause anyone not grouped with the caster to flee in terror in a random
direction.
===========================================================================
