COMMANDS (General Information)
===========================================================================
&+WMovement:&n                           | &+mCommunication:&n
NORTH SOUTH EAST WEST UP DOWN       | SAY ' SHOUT TELL ASK WHISPER
SLEEP WAKE REST SIT STAND FOLLOW    | GSAY SPEAK EMOTE IGNORE
KNEEL RECLINE ALERT DRAG            | PETITION 
