===========================================================================
Area of effect: <object> | <Room>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Temporary in Rooms, Permanent on items
Type of spell:  Enchantment

"Continual Light" allows the spell caster to enchant an item by granting it
its own light, making it a permanent light source. Not specifying an object
causes the whole room to be temporarily lit by a magical light.  
