COSMOMANCER (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The ultimate and most devastating Ethermancer specializes in the long 
forgotten and near shunned arts of cosmocy, the ability the control the 
planets and satellites themselves. By following this course in 
specialization the ethermancer loses some of his more spiritual powers, 
trading those in for pure offense. 

Spells 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
7th Circle : Cosmic Vacuum 
8th Circle : Ethereal Discharge 
9th Circle : Comet, Planetary Alignment 
11th Circle : Supernova 


===========================================================================
See also: ETHERMANCER, "COSMIC VACUUM", "ETHEREAL DISCHARGE", COMET, 
	  "PLANETARY ALIGNMENT", SUPERNOVA

#
CRAFTING
===========================================================================
Crafting is one of the primary skills of the Alchemist Class. By collecting
material pieces	from the corpses of dead mobs an alchemist can craft a wide 
range of equipment that can be used or sold at shops. 

Crafting explained:

With 1 material piece you can create small things like rings, earrings, etc.
With 2 material pieces you can create medium sized things like leggings,
       arm-plates, etc
With 3 material pieces you can create large items like cloaks and body
       armor.

Now you have your materials now what do you do? Select the materials you
want to use place them into your inventory and type:

     craft material object-type.
     
For example, if you have "a cracked magical gold piece" in your inventory
and type "craft gold ring" you may end up with a ring called "a crude
unique gold ring". 

Identifying the item after it is created will show you the stats. The
quality of the material used, your skill in crafting and your current level
all play a part in how powerful your newly crafted equipment becomes. We
are not giving out material formulas as it is a closely guarded alchemist
secret and nobody wants a guild of alchemists on their back. 
===========================================================================
See also: MIX, FORGE, SKILL_ALCHEMIST

#
"CREATE DRACOLICH" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <corpse>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Animation lasts until undead follower dies (again)
Type of spell:  Summoning

If the Necromancer has a suitable corpse at his feet, "Create Dracolich"
will transform the corpse into a powerful winged dragon. You can order a pet
dracolich to use the following special attacks:

-Roar
-Sweep (tail sweep)
-Breath (breath attack -i.e.: fire breath)

Effectiveness of some of these attacks may be hindered by the dracolich's
ability to maneuver whist in combat, and in the general struggle to obey
your commands they may pause from one instruction to another.

===========================================================================
See also: ORDER, PETS, PRESERVE, "MASS PRESERVE", EMBALM

