DARKNESS (Spell)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         inn darkness (for Drow Elf and Shades)
Area of Effect: <room>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Generic

This spell blankets the room in a cloak of magical darkness, through which
no light will penetrate. It will also dispel "Continual Light" spells in a
room. If this spell is cast upon a magically illuminating item, "Darkness"
will smother the light emanating from it.
===========================================================================
