#
DEFLECT (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster or until dispelled
Type of spell:  Protection

"Deflect" is a rather potent protectorate that reflects any spell cast at
the protected Mage back at the caster. The enemy caster then absorbs the
same adverse effects from the spell that he cast. "Deflect" will expire
after a successful attack from an offensive spell.
===========================================================================
See also: "ARCANE BLOCK"

#
DELIRIUM (Spell)
===========================================================================
The Illusionist is a master of deception and fallacy, both of which are
used by the Delirium spell to create a supreme spell of misdirection. A foe
targeted seemingly falls under a blanket of confusion and their ability to
deal with the simple reality of direction is lost.
===========================================================================
See also: ILLUSIONIST, SKILL_ILLUSIONIST

#
DELETE REROLL (General Information)
===========================================================================
Player files can be deleted at the login menu. Once a character is deleted,
you can NOT get it back. You may have several characters and often times
people reroll their stats until they end up with stats that please them.
===========================================================================
See also: STATS, CLASSES, RACES, REIMBURSEMENT

