#
DEXTERITY (General Information)
===========================================================================
Dexterity is a measure of deftness and hand/eye coordination, the ability
to use your hands well. It is the primary attribute of Rogues and Fighters.
Assassins and Thieves require dexterity for skills such as "Backstab" and
"Steal". Whereas, Fighter types need dexterity to successfully "Bash" their
opponents.
===========================================================================
See also: "SPELL, DEXTERITY", "ENHANCE DEXTERITY", STATISTICS

#
DIABOLIS (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The Diabolis Necromancer is a master of assembling and leading the most 
deadly of undead armies. They can exhume corpses from the ground to be used
at their disposal. The Reaper also has the chance to "Mummify", or embalm,
a corpse if they score the killing blow. 

Skills
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
