===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster> & <player> or <mob>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Teleportation

"Dimension Door" creates a short-lived extra dimensional corridor that 
allows the caster to teleport to any player or mob within that zone without 
possibility of arriving in the wrong place. This spell is distance-specific 
and can only be used within a certain number of rooms dependant on the 
proficiency of the caster.
