DRAG (Command)
===========================================================================
Syntax:  drag <object> <direction>

This command allows you to drag takeable objects, corpses, a sleeping, 
paralyzed, bound or mortally wounded person from room to room. It is good 
for hauling objects that are otherwise too heavy to move. Dragging items 
costs a lot of movement points however.
===========================================================================

