Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     N/A
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Generic

When cast, "Dragon" creates a illusionary red dragon that attacks the 
victim. The illusion will end when the victim or caster dies or the
duration of the spell ends. The illusion will also end after it has taken
enough damage. If the victim try s to flee the area the dragon
will attempt to hunt them down!
===========================================================================

