#
FISHING (Skill)
===========================================================================
Syntax: <fish> while standing on water.

The lakes and oceans of Duris are like most oceans filled with creatures 
that live in them. Using a standard fishing pole the creatures of Duris 
can attempt to catch fish and sea food. The chance of catching something
is dependant on the skill of the person and chance. The fish and sea food 
will increase the hitpoint regeneration and sometimes movement 
regeneration for a period of time. The duration and speed depends on what 
type of fish or sea food that was consumed. 

There are different types that can be caught are the following. Please 
note that they are now listed in order of how good they are.

a large bass
a piranha
a medium sized cod
a large pike fish
an impressive lobster
a large hairy crab
a large shrimp
a large flat oyster
a small clam
a large mussel
===========================================================================

#
"FIST OF DRAGON"
===========================================================================
The monk harnesses his inner chi-powers using it to cause his hands to 
harden. For the duration the monk can apply full force while hitting on 
creatures with protective spells, such as stone skin, rendering this type 
of defense useless. The duration of the chant goes up as the skill of the 
monk improves.
===========================================================================
See also: Monk

