FLAME  (General Information)
===========================================================================
To "flame" someone is to insult them without provocation.  Due to Duris 
competitive nature, occasional "flaming" is to be expected, though rampant 
flaming is discouraged and in some cases moderated.
===========================================================================
See also: KENON

