#
HEADBUTT (Skill)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         headbutt <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes

When successful, a headbutt will cause a sizable amount of damage to the 
enemy with the possibility of knocking them unconscious. If unsuccessful,
the initiator will take a sizable amount of damage himself with the 
possibility of knocking himself unconscious.
===========================================================================

