#
HELP (General Information)
===========================================================================
The "help" command lets you access things like this entry. Type "help"
alone to see a list of major topics.
===========================================================================
See also: VERSION

#
HIDE (Skill)
===========================================================================

Hide -Rogue Class Skill
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Syntax:         hide

"Hide" allows you to cleverly conceal yourself from the occupants of a room, 
regardless of whether they are other players or creatures. As with the 
"Sneak" command, there is always a chance that you will not hide 
successfully and your failure to do so will not be obvious to you. If your
attempt to hide is successful, you can only be detected by "Sense Life", 
"Infravision" or "Faerie Fog" . To break the hiding, issue any command. The 
effect will wear off after a period of time.

Hide -General Command
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Syntax:         hide <object>

Hide is a command you can use to conceal an object within the room. The
object you are trying to hide must be dropped and on the floor of the room
before you can conceal it. When you "look", this item should no longer 
appear in the room. You may "search" the room to re-discover the hidden 
item.

===========================================================================
See also: SEARCH, "SENSE LIFE", "FAERIE FOG", INFRAVISION

#
HITALL (Skill)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         hitall          : hit aggressive monsters
                hitall all      : hit all monsters

This skill allows you to hit all foes in the room simultaneously. Each
target may be hit once and only once, regardless of proficiency in "dual 
wield" or "double attack."  Using "hitall", will cause you to be stunned for
several rounds of combat, with the amount depending on how many targets you
attempted to hit.
===========================================================================
See also: "DOUBLE ATTACK", "DUAL WIELD"

#
HOLYMAN (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The Holyman Cleric is a master of defensive capabilities. He has the
ability to invoke his God to calm a room, when needed. And, under the
effect of the spell "Lesser Sanctuary", the Healer will take less physical
damage than normal. When soulshielded, it is said that mysterious things
may happen.

Innate Abilities
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
30th level:     Calm God Call

Spells
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
11th circle:    Lesser Sanctuary

===========================================================================
See also: CLERIC, "GOD CALL", "LESSER SANCTUARY"

