#
LUCK (General Information)
===========================================================================
Luck is the chance of good things happening to you; how much good fortune 
or prosperity you may have. Alchemists are the class primarily in need of
luck for skills such as "Forage" and "Craft". All other races and classes 
benefit from luck as well. When you have high luck, things will more often
go your way.
===========================================================================
See also: STATISTICS, SERENDIPITY

#
"MAGE FLAME" (Spell)
