#
MANA (General Information)
===========================================================================
A number of classes on Duris still use the mana system (rather than the
memorize system).  What this means is rather than praying or memorizing
for spell slots, each spell takes a specific number of mana to cast.  If
the caster runs out of mana, or exceeds him/herself when casting a spell,
he/she will pass out for a short period of time.  
===========================================================================
See also: PSIONICIST, COMMUNE

#
MANGLE
===========================================================================
With their heightened battle senses, the Mauler is more able to take
advantage of their opponents misadventure. A Mauler's power comes
from the hate building within himself, while in combat some Mauler's
become so angered from their opponents attacks that they may strike back
at the opponents arm, possibly dislodging their weapon.
===========================================================================
See also: MAULER, BOILING BLOOD, SPEC_LIST, BERSERKER, SKILL_BERSERKER

#
MAULER (Specialization)
===========================================================================
As the name implies, Mauler's have increased their skills when it comes
to the control of their takedown skills. With the enhanced ability to
channel these skills, they have learnt to automatically to recover more 
quickly when they use their skill to take down an opponent. It is also 
said that Mauler's focus so intensely upon attacking their opponents that 
some seem to not even feel pain when attacked. It's also been rumored 
that some Mauler's have been angered so badly that they have been known to 
nearly rip the an opponents weapon and arm from it's socket.

Skills
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
41st Level:   Boiling Blood
51st Level:   Mangle

===========================================================================
See also: MANGLE, "BOILING BLOOD", SPEC_LIST, BERSERKER, SKILL_BERSERKER

#
MAP
===========================================================================
By typing map from any location on Duris, you will see a rough map of the
parts of the world currently under the control of the races that you are
a member of, or their allies.  For example, if you are a human and type map
you will see the northern sections of the world.  If you are a troll, you
will see the southern part of the world.
===========================================================================

#
MARTIAL ARTS
===========================================================================
This skill measures how skilled a monk is at using his body as a weapon.
Until his martial arts skill is well practiced, he will not be able to deal
out as much damage with his bare hands and feet.
===========================================================================

