"MASS HEAL" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <room>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     Yes
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Healing

"Mass Heal" heals anyone and anything in the same room as the caster, for
the same as a regular "Heal" spell.
===========================================================================
See also: HEAL, "NEGATIVE ENERGY VORTEX"

#
"MASS INVISIBILITY" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <room>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Enchantment

The caster attempts to cast "Improved Invisibility" on every creature in 
the room, including himself/herself. All loose objects laying around in the 
room will also turn invisible.
===========================================================================
