"MIND BLANK" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     N/A
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster.
Type of Spell:  Enchantment

This spell has the unique ability to mentally cloak the caster by altering
the perception of all who would gaze upon him. Since the victims mind
itself is being altered, all detection magics have no effect on the ability
to perceive the caster.
===========================================================================

