"NEGATIVE ENERGY VORTEX" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <room>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Healing

This spell creates an enormous vortex that links directly to the negative
material plane. All of the casters' enemies are sucked in for a split
second and subjected to the ravaging effects of the raw negative energy
bombardment. The casters' allies then gain the energy that their enemies
have lost.
===========================================================================
See also: "MASS HEAL"

