===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Generic

This spell is rather potent when used outdoors. "Pass Without Trace" 
enables you to efficiently cover your tracks while moving. You will also be 
almost impossible to see from a long distance away.

NOTE: This spell can only be effective when cast on a medium sized or 
      smaller person.
===========================================================================

#
PASSWORD
===========================================================================
The "password" option, seen at the entry menu, allows you to change your
character's password. Players should make it a rule to change their 
passwords often to avoid the unpleasantness of having someone else gain 
control of their character. It is the players' responsibility to safeguard 
themselves by ensuring that they use a different password on each MUD they 
log into. Gods are *not* responsible for any "hacked" or "stolen" 
characters.
===========================================================================
See also: RULES, REIMBURSEMENT

#
"PATH OF FROST" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Enchantment

"Path of Frost" causes the Ethermancer's wings to start flapping rapidly,
creating icy frost that freezes very ground they walk on.
===========================================================================

