#
PICK LOCKS (Skill)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         pick <door_name | container_name>
Aggressive:     No

You may use this skill for picking locks, but you should remember that not
all locks can be picked. Also, lock picks tend to be very fragile. Bring an
extra set. You MUST have a set of lock-picks to be able to attempt picking
a lock.

Examples:
> pick door
> pick safe
===========================================================================
See also: OPEN CLOSE LOCK UNLOCK

#
PIPER "UNHOLY-PIPER" (Sub-Class of: Rogue)
===========================================================================
Blessed with the talent of music, pipers can, with practice, play any
instrument. These instruments can invoke magical tunes and songs that act
as spells, aiding a party during their adventures. Pipers are a thief/mage/
warrior hybrid by nature, and possess some of the advantages of all of
those classes. They are true "Jacks of all Trade" which means they have
many skills and spells, but are master of none.  

Allowable races:        Vampire, Lich, Shadow Beast.
Equipment Usage:        Like all classes on Duris, Pipers have their own set
                        of equipment they can use. Pipers can use most
                        weapons, and armor, also many magic items.
                        
===========================================================================
See also: PRACTICE, ROGUE, SKILL_PIPER, SONGS, WAIL

#
PLAGUE (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Healing

"Plague" will temporarily cause the victim to receive less benefit from all
healing spells.
===========================================================================

#
"PLANE SHIFT" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         inn plane <planename>
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Teleportation

"Plane Shift" transports the caster instantly to another plane of existence.  
The shift is a one way trip and does now allow for a return home, except by 
another means of teleportation.

The planes that may be shifted to are:

	-&+yThe Elemental Plane Of Earth&N
	-&+bThe Elemental Plane Of Water&N
	-&+CThe Elemental Plane Of Air&N
	-&+rThe Elemental Plane Of Fire&N
	-&+RThe Plane Of Avernus On The Nine Hells&N
	-&+LThe Negative Material Plane&N
	-&+LThe Ethereal Plane&N
	-The Astral Plane

&+RWarning:&n Shifting can be dangerous, as you just may land on a aggro
        mob!
===========================================================================
See also: GATE

#
"PLANETARY ALIGNMENT" (Spell) 
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <self> 
Aggressive: no 
Cumulative: no 
Duration: Instantaneous 
