PLAY (Skill)
===========================================================================
Syntax:         play <song_name>
Aggressive:     Dependent on s ng sung

To create magical effects, the bard must hold the proper instrument, then 
"play" the appropriate song. A magical song will not work without the 
proper instrumental accompaniment. To end a song simply type "play."
===========================================================================
See also: INSTRUMENT, SONG, WAIL

