#
POISON (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim> | <object>
Aggressive:     Yes (on victim)
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster for victims,
                Permanent for objects

Casting "Poison" on a victim will cause them to suffer slight damage every 
hour and heal more slowly than usual.

NOTE: The spell "Remove Poison" neutralizes the poison, magical or not.
===========================================================================
See also: "REMOVE POISON"

