#
POUR (General Information)
===========================================================================
Syntax:  pour <from-drink_container> <to-drink_container | 'out'>


         Examples:

         pour skin out
         pour bottle barrel


Use "pour" if you wish to transfer liquid from one drink container to
another or empty a drink container completely.  Note that you cannot
mix liquids.
===========================================================================
See also: EAT DRINK SIP TASTE, FILL

