"POWER WORD BLIND" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Permanent until healed
Type of spell:  Generic

This spell permanently blind a victim with less than certain amount of
life force, with the amount determined by the spellcaster's
proficiency. The blindness can only be removed via a "Cure Blind" or more
powerful healing spell.
===========================================================================
See also: BLINDNESS, "CURE BLIND", "FULL HEAL"

#
"POWER WORD KILL" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Generic

This spell causes instant death to a victim with less than a certain amount 
of lifeforce, with the amount determined by the spellcaster's proficiency.  
It has no effect on a victim with more lifeforce.
===========================================================================

