#
PSIONICIST (Sub-Class of: Magic-User)
===========================================================================
Psionicist are a class that has amazing control over their minds, allowing
them to master the hidden power of the mind itself.  Psionicist can use
this power to advance their causes, whatever those may be.  A Psionicist
must have an amazing intelligence.  Psionicist's abilities are similar to
the alien Illithid Mindflayer, but not identical.

Allowable races: Githyanki, Phantom.
Equipment usage: Psionicists have their own classification of item
                 restrictions. While they are somewhat limited in their
                 choice of weapons or armor, they can use almost all
                 magical items.       
===========================================================================
See also: GITHYANKI, MAGIC-USER, SKILL_PSIONICIST

#
PSYCHEPORTER (Specialization)
===========================================================================
Some Psionicists grow bored with the inability to efficiently travel between
the planes, therefore a small sect has chosen to enhance their transit
abilities. These astral travelers, or Psycheporters, have many means of
improved transit at their disposal. They have also learned a means to travel
on their native plane with little or no threat to themselves.

Skills
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
none!

Innate Abilities
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
30th level:     astral affinity
46th level:     spacial focus

Spells
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
12th circle:   thought beacon

===========================================================================
See also: PSIONICIST, WILL, SPACIAL FOCUS, ASTRAL AFFINITY, TELEPORT,
IMPROVED WORMHOLE, THOUGHT BEACON

#
"PSYCHIC CRUSH" "IMPROVED PSYCHIC CRUSH" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Generic

"Psychic Crush" viciously and directly attacks the victim's physical as
well as his metaphysical mind. The combined attacks result in severe damage
and other unfortunate aftereffects. A psionicist specializing as an 
enslaver will upon the attack try to penetrate the inner defenses of the 
mind and deliver yet another crippling attack.
===========================================================================

