#
REIMBURSEMENT (General Information)
===========================================================================
We now only grant reimbursements for corrupt player files or a bug that
causes complete equipment loss on multiple characters. There will be &+RNO
EXCEPTIONS&N.

We will &+RNOT&N grant reimbursements for fumbled weapons, lost or stolen
items, decayed corpses, hacked accounts, changes to the game, things lost
during a crash or reboot, or anything that does not fall under the above
two exceptions.
===========================================================================
See also: LINK, CRASH, REBOOT, POLICIES

