Type of spell:  Generic

This spell will remove a "curse" on any person or item. To remove a curse 
on a person caused by an object, the person must first consent you. Once
you cast the spell on them, the cursed item will drop from their inventory.
You must then pick up that item and re-cast the spell on the object 
directly.
