"ROPE TRICK" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Type of spell:  Enchantment

This spell makes the victim concealed from all occupants in the room,
regardless of whether they are other players or creatures. Once hidden, 
you can only be detected by "Sense Life", "Infravision" or "Faerie Fog". 
To break the hiding, issue any command. The effect will wear off after a 
period of time.
===========================================================================
