#
SOCIETY
===========================================================================
Association Command

Syntax:   society <s>ubcommands argumentlist

(Subcommands can be accessed by just using the first letter.)


List of subcommands
-------------------

&+Wsociety&n
soc -displays a list of members and various info about them depending
      on your rank. Members higher in rank than you are only shown if online.
      Also displays some info on the association to higher ranks.
      Finally it gives a list of people ostracized by your association.

&+Wsociety apply member&n
soc a Hero -applies to the (senior or higher) member Hero of an association
             for membership in his association.
soc a me -clears an existing application to an association.

&+Wsociety enroll applicant&n
soc e Newone -enrolls Newone to the association, if he has applied for
               membership first.

&+Wsociety kickout member&n
soc k Twink -kicks member Twink out of the association, erasing his name
              in the member list. Is also used to delete names from the
              ostracism list.

&+Wsociety secede [confirm]&n
soc s -just displays a warning message that "soc s confirm" has to be typed
soc s confirm -the member leaves the association. All his data is erased
                from the member list -except if he was a declared enemy.
                Then he is automatically put on the ostracism list.

&+Wsociety ostracize name&n
soc o Anti -puts the name "Anti" on the ostracism list. The association's
             guards will then attack any person with the name "Anti" as
             if they had the rank enemy in the association.

&+Wsociety rank name change&n
soc r Lucky 2 -the member Lucky is promoted by two ranks.
soc r Noluck -3 -the member Noluck is demoted by three ranks.
                   Note that the minimum mortal rank obtainable with this
                   normal (member) and the maximum is leader.

&+Wsociety punish name&n
soc p Arrggh -the first punish puts member Arrggh on parole.
soc p Arrggh -the second one declares Arrggh as enemy, thus making the
               association guards aggressive to him. The rank subcommand
               (see above) can be used to reinstate Arrggh, but only a
               leader can do this once he is of enemy rank.

&+Wsociety challenge member&n
soc c Bigger -(this is not allowed by all association) this challenges a
               member of the next higher rank for his position. This is
               a political command, there is no auto-attack. The outcome
               of the challenge depends mainly on experience and the
               looser faces tough penalties.

&+Wsociety name rank_keyword new_rank_name&n
soc n enemy Hunted by -the new rank name of the enemy rank is "Hunted by".
                        A list of rank_keywords and current names for them
                        is shown to the leader with the "soc" list.
soc n l Master of -the rank keywords can be abbreviated as well, here "l"
                    stands for leader rank, now called "Master of".
soc n normal -without a new rank name, the rank name is wiped and in the
               title only the association name is shown.
               ANSI can be used in rank names. Note that the association name
               is pasted directly behind the rank name, so often a trailing
               space is necessary in the given rank name.

&+Wsociety home&n
soc h -set your hometown and birthplace to your guild hall. You must be 
        inside your hall for it to work.

* The following money commands accept multiple arguments for "money" and
* the coin type is determined by the first letter only. So a valid
* example would be: "10 plat 2 gc 3 s 5 copper".

&+Gsociety fine name money&n
soc f Wrong 20 p 10 sc -issues a fine of 20 platinum and 10 silver coins to
                         member Wrong of the association.
soc f Wrong -30 plat -subtracts 30 plat from the debt Wrong has. If he has
                       less than 30 p debts, then his debt is set to zero.
soc f all 20 gold -issues a fine of 20 gold (for example as membership fee)
                    to everybody. Note that one can fine only lower ranks, so
                    in truth this would give only fines to all lower ranks.

&+Gsociety deposit money&n
soc d 12 platinum 30 cc -deposits 12 plat and 30 copper into the association
                          account. Any debts the member has are lessened
                          accordingly. This subcommand can be used by
                          applicants to pay an entrance fee.

&+Wsociety withdraw money&n
soc w 100 plat -withdraws 100 platinum coins from the association account.

&+Wsociety title name new_title
soc t billybob &+YCorn&+WHusker &+CSupreme&n -sets BillyBob's 'rank'
title to CornHusker Supreme.  this title is never overwritten by new
rank titles as long as the "no title change" toggle is set (see below).
this command can only be used by guild leaders (to title other players),
or deputies and officers (to title themselves).

&+Wsociety toggle_title_flag
soc g -toggles your 'no title change' flag
===========================================================================
See also: CONSTRUCT, GUILD, GUILDHALL, "SOCIETY EXAMPLES", TITLE

#
"SOCIETY EXAMPLES"
===========================================================================

Becoming a founding leader:

1) soc secede -to secede from the association one is joined up in
2) soc apply me -to clear applications to other associations
3) decide on the association name and whether challenge will be allowed
4) talk to association god(s).

Note that 1) and 2) can be skipped if one isn't member/applicant.

Typical enrolment procedure (Aguy is non-member, Bguy is senior member):

Aguy: ' I would like to join.
Bguy: ' Ok, entrance fee is 10 plat.
Bguy: society   *To check how much money the association has now.*
Aguy: society apply Bguy   *Aguy is now applicant to Bguy's association.*
Aguy: society deposit 10 plat   *Aguy pays entrance fee.*
Aguy: ' Ok, I paid up.
Bguy: society   *To check that statement*.
Bguy: society enroll Aguy   *Enroll Aguy to the association as normal member.*

Note that Aguy pays to the association, not to Bguy, to avoid fraud.

Officer Aguy wants to issue a general membership fee of 1 plat, fine Bguy
10 plat and keep Cguy completely free of debt (Cguy has no debt up to now):

Aguy: society fine all 1 p   *Fines only members with lower rank!*
Aguy: society fine Bguy 10 p   *Bguy now has at least a debt of 11 plat.*
Aguy: society fine Cguy -20 p   *Subtracts 20 p from Cguy's debt, wiping it.*

Leader Bigone and Deputy Notsobig disagree on treating Member Twink:

Bigone: society punish Twink   *Puts Twink on parole*
Notsobig: society rank Twink +1   *Twink is normal member again.*
Bigone: tell Notsobig WTF?
Bigone: society punish Twink   *He is on parole again.*
Bigone: society punish Twink   *Now he is enemy, Notsobig can't lift that.*
Bigone: society fine Notsobig 100 plat   *Notsobig is in trouble...*
Notsobig: ' You are going down!   *Notsobig is in same room as Bigone.*
Notsobig: society challenge Bigone   *Say he wins the challenge.*
Notsobig: society kickout Bigone   *Notsobig is the leader now: Bye, bye...*
Notsobig: society rank Twink +5   *He makes Twink Deputy.*
Bigone: ' Hah!
Bigone: kill Notsobig    *Say he wins and Notsobig looses lots of Exp.*
Twink: society challenge Notsobig   *Twink exploits that to become leader.*
Twink: society rank Notsobig -3   *He really is an a... .*
Twink: ' Bigone, 20 plat to me and you are back in.   *Etc.*

Leader Dumbone changes names of some ranks:

Dumbone: society name leader Archmage of    *Note: add a trailing space.*
Dumbone: society name normal   *No name means only association name is shown.*
Dumbone: society name god Stupid one of   *He can't do it anyway, but...*
God: tell Dumbone Nice try, goodbye.   *... a god caught him trying.*
God: society punish Dumbone    *Dumbone is made enemy and since he is in
God: society punish Dumbone     guildhall the guards kill him.*

<Note -gods can access all your mortal commands and outrank everybody!
Furthermore gods can BAN a mortal from all associations -this happens
to Dumbone now after the god had his fun having him killed.>
===========================================================================
See also: SOCIETY, ASSOCIATIONS, GUILDHALL, GUILD

#
"SOLAR FLARE" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     Yes
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Fire

This spell sends waves of white hot flames at the intended victim, 
causing considerable damage.
===========================================================================

#
SONGS
===========================================================================
These are the basic skills of the bard and spectral piper, and have various 
magical
properties.  Certain songs are only effective on certain instruments.

6th level:      song of sleep (Flute)
                piper: elegy of nightmares (Flute)
16th level:     song of calming (Harp)
                piper: funereal hymn (Harp)
                song of discord (Flute}
                song of harmony (Flute)
21st level:     song of protection (Horn)
                piper: dirge of bones (Horn)
                song of forgetfulness (Mandolin)
                piper: hymn of the zombie (Mandolin)
                song of cowardice (Drums)
                piper: terrorizing rhythms (Drums)
26th level:     song of peace (Harp)
                piper: requiem of the crypts (Harp)
31st level:     song of flight (Horn)
                piper: dirge of the ghosts (Horn)
                song of dragons (Horn)
                piper: draconic crescendo (Horn)
36th level:     song of healing (Lyre)
                piper: song of the unholy (Lyre)
                song of harming (Flute)
                piper: song of decay (Lyre)
41st level:     song of storms (Drums)
                piper: chime of the vampire (Drums)
46th level:     song of heroism (Drums)
                piper: stanza of the fury (Drums)
                song of revelation (Mandolin)
                piper: hymn of morbid visions (Mandolin)
                song of chaos (Drums)
                piper: song of the night (Drums)
51st level:     song of charming (Flute)
                piper: chant of subversion (Flute)
===========================================================================
See also: INSTRUMENT, PLAY, BARD, SKILL_BARD, WAIL, PIPER, SKILL_PIPER

