"SOUL TRAP" (Skill)
===========================================================================
With macabre thirst, the Deathlord thrusts its weapon through the still
warm corpse of its ally's foe, seeking the very soul of the fallen. Drawing
the essence of the shadow of the being out, it embraces that life-force,
taking the potency for its own.
===========================================================================
