With the power of this ability, the Psycheporter can open his mind to a
much wider range of wormhole targets within a certain distance. They have 
also learned more ways to sustain their wormholes for longer periods, 
therefore they can handle a greater volume of travelers for a longer period 
of time. 
===========================================================================
