"SPINAL CORRUPTION" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     Yes
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Enchantment

Using the power of his mind, the caster disrupts the victims' brains'
ability to communicate with the rest of his central nervous system.
This causes the victim to have trouble travelling about, and
in extreme cases, makes it harder for them to escape from combat.
===========================================================================

#
SPIRITMASTER (MultiClass)
===========================================================================
A Spiritmaster is a multi-class Shaman/Cleric.

Notes on Spiritmaster:
Shamans use totems, and memorize spells without spellbooks.
Clerics pray, and require no spellbooks or totems.
If you start as a Shaman, you will memorize spells, but you will no longer
need totems, for ANY of your spells.
If you start as a Cleric, you will pray spells, but again, you will not
need totems, for ANY of your spells.
===========================================================================
See Also: SHAMAN, CLERIC, MULTI-CLASS, PRAY, MEMORIZE

#
SPIRITUALIST (Specialization)
===========================================================================
The Spiritualist has mastered the art of both life and death. He is able to
heal more effectively than his other Shaman counterparts. Having seen 
beyond death, the Spiritualist cannot be shaken by mortal intimidation. It 
is even said that at the highest form of their art, they can even stave off 
death itself!

Innate Abilities
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
36th level:     Improved Heal
56th level:     Resurrection

Spells
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
7th circle:     Indomitability
10th circle:    Spirit Walk

===========================================================================
See also: "IMPROVED HEAL", INDOMITABILITY, "SPIRIT WALK", RESURRECTION, 
          SHAMAN

