#
"VAPOR STRIKE" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Protection

"Vapor Strike" grants the victim an added hitroll, the amount of increased
hitroll varies randomly.
===========================================================================

#
"VENTRILOQUATE" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim> | <object>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     N/A
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Generic
Syntax:         cast 'ventriloquate' <victim | object> <text>

All those in the room falling to the caster's enchantment will believe
that the victim or object has spoken the desired text.
===========================================================================

