"VIGORIZE CRITIC" (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <victim>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     Yes
Duration:       Instantaneous
Type of spell:  Enchantment

This handy spell restores to the victim some movement, letting him or her 
travel farther. The amount of movement restored is dependent on the version 
of the spell cast. "Vigorize Critic" is more powerful than its counterparts, 
"Vigorize Light" and "Vigorize Serious".
===========================================================================
