#
VINES (Spell)
===========================================================================
Area of effect: <caster>
Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Protection

The spell "Vines" encases the Druid in a shell of vines grown from herbs. 
When successful, the vines will absorb damage from magical or physical 
attacks. But, if the Druid moves, the vines will instantly rot and fade 
away. 

NOTE: You must have at least (one) herb in your inventory, in order for
this spell to take effect.
===========================================================================
See also: FORAGE, INGREDIENTS

