Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependent on proficiency of caster
Type of spell:  Generic

When cast, "Wall of Stone" will block an exit to a room in the direction 
the caster has specified. No one will be able to enter or exit the room 
until the wall is dispelled, hit or its duration runs out.
