Aggressive:     No
Cumulative:     No
Duration:       Dependant upon level of caster
Type of spell:  Enchantment

"Wandering Woods" can deceive and confuse when cast in a natural setting.
It creates the illusion of surreal forest in the immediate area, causing
anyone within its effects to lose their sense of direction.
